{"tid":1195104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六九遊行入夜行動","createTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T14:15:16.000Z","uid":70403,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75f6ac76173438e3fee0c9bd7d9cef3a1ccfc923","tid":1195104,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">男人要留守，入夜需要你</span></strong></span><br />\n家長帶住小朋友或者有長有幼嘅香港人開始離去，<br />\n佢地嘅責任完成架啦，冇可能要求老幼留守。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">匹夫有責，唔好以為行完就搞掂<br />\n！！！條例尚未撤回架！！！<br />\n隨時有勇武行動，唔衝唔緊要<br />\n不過要拉住前線，唔好俾人夾走</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">萬事小心，六九未完</div></span><br />\n警方應該等小朋友，老人家散哂就開始行動。<br />\n大家記住睇住自己人，唔好走散。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6daa0c9b6612aafe4fd1e8cfec90ce4e2629e60","tid":1195104,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"民陣走啦 要衝架喇唔衝就無人"},{"pid":"11cb26a228022150474f980e1a5be3727f1bba3d","tid":1195104,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"遇到暴力 請團結對抗"},{"pid":"b53f8e04b8fc15e0fea3d947c026efb66680b41f","tid":1195104,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11cb26a228022150474f980e1a5be3727f1bba3d","tid":1195104,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"遇到暴力 請團結對抗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"566688a462036aa7f837b5011b24e542b0f42921","tid":1195104,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"深夜／清晨輪替記住小心。<br />\n記得唔好用八達通，最好帶衣物替換，<br />\n唔好打卡，有需要買張新 sim 卡。<br />\n<br />\n食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaf111f9ab052f4e593f12afe